Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:37.49,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:94908,97493}{\i1}Nozomi's older brother\Nhad reappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:40.99,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:97493,100997}{\i1}When Nozomi found out about it\Nand that he was going to America,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:43.70,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:100997,103708}{\i1}she went to the Yokohama Port\Nto see him for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:51.96,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:104542,111966}{\i1}But the one aboard the ship was surprisingly\NFanni Moriyama, who had recently disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:57.84,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:111966,117847}{\i1}Not knowing that her brother is\Nactually him, Nozomi's world has turned gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:08.90,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:126314,128900}{\i1}There's nothing good about\Na canary that forgot its song.{NOTE:歌を忘れたカナリヤに\\N魅力はない\\N栄光にむかって\\Nはばたくことを\\N忘れないでくれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:11.61,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:128900,131611}{\i1}Work hard and become\Na great singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:23.08,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:139953,143081}{\i1}You're right, Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:24.99,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:143081,144999}{\i1}But why did you leave for America?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:27.29,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:146084,147293}Fanni…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:34.84,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:151256,154842}I wonder if Hisashi was\Nthere as well, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:37.92,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:155343,157929}I bet you're still thinking about\Nyour boyfriend, Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:39.01,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:157929,159013}No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:41.34,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:159013,161349}I'm so jealous, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:43.55,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:161349,163559}I want to fall in love, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:46.31,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:163559,166312}I'm sure you'll meet\Na wonderful man some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:47.77,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:166312,167772}A pie in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:49.60,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:167772,169607}– Give it time.\N– I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:50.73,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:169607,170733}Alright, time to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:03:01.74,Default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:174696,181744}{\fad(300,300)\t(6299,7799,3,\1c&H101010&\3c&H101010&\4c&H101010&)}— Episode 10 —\NA Journey Towards Tomorrow{NOTE:第10話\\Nあすへの旅立ち}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.87,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:187083,188876}I'm sorry.\NI'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:10.33,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:188876,190336}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:17.09,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:192630,197093}You just can't get over how\NI take classes from Mr. Egawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:19.34,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:197093,199345}That's enough, Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:22.93,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:200346,202932}You shouldn't descend to the level\Nof arguing with a maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:23.76,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:202932,203766}But, Mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:27.81,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:204642,207812}Even if she takes classes as well,\Nshe's still just a servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:32.27,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:207812,212275}You will become a star soon, so you need\Nto be careful how you behave around people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:38.44,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:217071,218448}You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.32,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:222452,224329}Good day, Mr. Egawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:45.03,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:224329,225038}It's me, Kōda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.75,0:03:51.29,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:228750,231294}{\i1}You think you're better?\NWait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.88,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:231961,234881}Here is a small\Ntoken of our gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:56.63,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:235798,236632}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:04:01.84,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:237216,241846}I heard that you fly to Europe soon.\NI thought about helping with the expenses a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:05.64,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:241846,245641}I am going there to spectate\Nat a music festival as part of my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:09.72,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:247060,249729}It is a private trip.\NI cannot accept money from anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.98,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:250772,252982}Oh, please don't be\Nso formal, Maestro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:16.44,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:252982,256444}You can have it.\NWe only have a small favor to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:17.44,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:256444,257445}Let's hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:20.86,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:257445,260865}I would like to be introduced\Nat Uchida Productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:22.36,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:260865,262367}Uchida Productions?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:26.03,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:262367,266037}In order to be a professional singer,\Nyou need a recording company, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:29.04,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:266037,269040}Since we're at it, we might\Nas well go with the best one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.83,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:271376,273836}Uchida Productions\Nmake the top of the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:37.54,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:273836,277548}I don't think they'd come to regret\Nsigning a contract with our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:41.26,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:277548,281260}I don't think you're aware of how intense\Nthe competition is in that world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:44.34,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:281260,284347}I think a small but effective company\Nwould be a better choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:47.18,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:284347,287183}All you have to do\Nis to introduce her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:52.39,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:289268,292397}Don't worry about the money,\NI will cover all the costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:54.77,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:293314,294774}Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:58.82,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:294774,298820}There are things in this world\Nthat money cannot buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:05:00.65,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:298820,300655}I wonder about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:12.46,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:305835,312467}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Music is my friend  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:17.76,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:312467,317764}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  When things get hard, it stays—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:18.53,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:317764,318531}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.85,0:05:27.52,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:324854,327523}What's wrong?\NDon't hold back, continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:32.52,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:329066,332528}You have a pretty\Ngood voice. I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:36.86,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:332528,336866}It has a beautiful feeling to it and\Ncomes from a very charming pair of lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:42.45,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:339827,342455}Ow! You have very soft hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:47.79,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:342455,347794}Nohara-san, this is not a place for guests.\NPlease wait at the entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.79,0:05:50.88,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:347794,350880}Oh, boy, here goes\Nthe watchdog.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:52.21,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:350880,352215}See you some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:54.55,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:353174,354550}What a skirt chaser.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:55.80,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:354550,355802}Nohara?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:58.13,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:355802,358137}As in the famous lyricist,\NNohara Jun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.13,0:06:00.22,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:358137,360223}Yes. He's a bad womanizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:01.55,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:360223,361557}Better watch out for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:03.55,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:361557,363559}I think he has a thing for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:05.26,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:363559,365269}Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:06.52,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:365269,366521}He was just flirting with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.53,0:06:17.57,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:375530,377573}The lyrics, you want them\Nfor this kid's debut?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:20.91,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:377573,380910}Yes. What do you think?\NI think she has a rather pleasant voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:24.58,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:380910,384580}With your writing\Nshe should be quite successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:30.04,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:388584,390044}Alright. When?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:33.42,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:390044,393422}How about after I return from Europe?\NYou'll have enough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:39.01,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:395967,399011}After seeing the girl,\Nhow can I refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:42.09,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:399011,402098}So, Mr. Nohara,\Nyou agree to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.09,0:06:46.51,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:402098,406519}Of course you will be well rewarded,\Ndo not have the slightest doubt about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:53.65,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:408688,413651}By the way, who is this beautiful lady\Nwho sings like a bird in your garage?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.65,0:06:55.73,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:413651,415736}Oh? You mean Mine Nozomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.73,0:06:57.94,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:415736,417947}The one with the sexy jeans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:06:59.65,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:417947,419657}Yes, Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:02.49,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:419657,422493}I've already put my eyes on her,\Nbut she's not ready yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:04.20,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:422493,424203}I was late, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:11.58,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:428875,431586}Sir, let's continue with the lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:12.75,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:431586,432753}Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.13,0:07:16.75,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:434130,436757}Rather than the usual song,\NI'd like to sing to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:22.51,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:440386,442513}Oh? Pretty confident, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:38.32,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:450605,458321}{\i1}Michiko wanted to make sure that both girls\Nwere indeed competing at Egawa Isao's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:41.69,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:458321,461699}{\i1}But at the entrance to Egawa's\Nresidence, she saw to her surprise
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:45.91,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:461699,465912}{\i1}the figure of Nohara Jun, her little brother\Nwho she had parted ways with five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.03,0:07:48.62,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:467038,468623}{\i1}Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:50.20,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:468623,470207}{\i1}What is Jun doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:56.83,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:474045,476839}Mr. Nohara, we have a chance\Nto get to know each other better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:59.59,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:476839,479592}What would you say to invite me\Nfor a nice ride in your car?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:02.09,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:480217,482094}You didn't feel comfortable\Naround your mom, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:06.80,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:485765,486807}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:09.47,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:486807,489477}Not at all.\NMy mom's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:11.52,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:489477,491520}– Where do you want to go?\N– I'll leave that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:13.52,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:491520,493522}Alright, let's get going, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.86,0:08:20.52,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:498861,500529}Please follow that red sports car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.40,0:08:22.57,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:501405,502573}{\i1}There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.57,0:08:24.61,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:502573,504617}{\i1}That was my little brother Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:50.60,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:529141,530601}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:52.10,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:530601,532103}Sorry, but could you get off now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:54.77,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:533312,534772}Why, all of the sudden…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:56.56,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:534772,536565}That's rather rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:57.81,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:536565,537817}Whatever, just get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:08:59.61,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:537817,539610}It's an urgent matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.90,0:09:03.11,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:540903,543114}How rude of you!\NWhat on earth is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.91,0:09:10.87,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:548911,550871}You can go home by taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:17.75,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:556252,557753}Who do they think they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:20.21,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:557753,560214}I'll make you pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:22.50,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:561048,562508}It's been a while, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:25.42,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:562508,565428}I haven't seen you for five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.42,0:09:27.51,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:565428,567513}What did you do all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:29.22,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:567513,569223}I succeeded, but it wasn't easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:36.64,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:572601,576647}There's no sunlight at all.\NWhat kind of place is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:40.15,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:576647,580151}I owe it to you that I couldn't\Nget out of this kind of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.15,0:09:43.15,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:580151,583154}When I left, I came to\Nwhere I am all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:45.15,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:583154,585156}So, what did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:49.61,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:585156,589618}You're clearly well acquainted with Egawa.\NYou must also know Mine Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:51.41,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:589618,591412}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.41,0:09:54.45,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:591412,594457}I'd like you to collect information\Non her from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:57.33,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:594457,597334}What? Did she do something to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:09:58.54,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:597334,598544}You could say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:10:00.75,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:598544,600755}I have a certain plan\Nwith her in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:03.79,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:601505,603799}What kind of plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:05.30,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:603799,605301}That doesn't concern you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:09.09,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:605301,609096}How do you expect me to help if I don't\Neven know what you're going to do, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.09,0:10:10.72,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:609096,610723}You sound kind of shady.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:15.10,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:612641,615102}Jun. You dare to lecture me\Nafter what you did to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.10,0:10:19.52,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:615102,619523}Remember that you left the house\Ntaking all my savings with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:24.44,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:620775,624445}It was all the money\NI'd sacrificed my youth for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:26.23,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:624445,626238}You used it as a stepping stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:29.03,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:626238,629033}You were able to succeed\Nonly because I gave up my youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:33.03,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:629617,633037}Ah, all right.\NI'll do what you've asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.04,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:640169,642046}– Have a safe trip!\N– Have a safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:43.67,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:642046,643672}Off he went!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.67,0:10:45.38,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:643672,645382}Let's can take it easy\Nwhile he's in Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:46.55,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:645382,646550}That's my girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:49.22,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:647051,649220}We're gonna have lots of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:00.18,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:658479,660189}Is this Egawa-san's residence?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:02.23,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:660189,662233}Yes, yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:04.77,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:662233,664777}Yes. I'm Mine Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.77,0:11:06.77,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:664777,666779}An accountant?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:08.69,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:666779,668697}What about my dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:10.28,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:668697,670282}It's about the\Nhospitalization expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:12.82,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:670282,672827}In case you don't cover\Nthe bill soon…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:13.82,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:672827,673828}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:17.03,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:673828,677039}I'm afraid he'll have to be moved\Nto another hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:19.54,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:677039,679542}Dad's going to get kicked out?\NThat's absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:22.50,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:680751,682503}I feel sorry for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:25.21,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:682503,685214}But unfortunately a hospital\Nisn't a charity organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:27.59,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:685214,687591}This is why you must pay\Nfor the care you get.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:32.05,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:687591,692054}A nurse had told me that the insurance\Nwill cover most of the expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:35.97,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:692054,695975}I cannot comment on what you have\Nbeen told, but rules are rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.97,0:11:39.39,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:695975,699395}I hate to say it, but your father\Nwill be forcibly discharged.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.56,0:11:41.73,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:700563,701730}Forcibly discharged?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.73,0:11:42.77,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:701730,702773}Forcibly discharged?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:43.81,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:702773,703816}Forcibly discharged?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.81,0:11:44.69,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:703816,704692}Forcibly discharged?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.69,0:11:45.86,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:704692,705860}Forcibly discharged?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:50.15,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:707611,710156}At any rate, please come\Nto the hospital as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.63,0:12:09.09,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:727631,729091}{\i1}Dad…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:11.09,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:729091,731093}{\i1}Dad's gonna get kicked out?
Comment: 0,0:12:17.08,0:12:17.08,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:737082,737082}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:21.96,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:737208,741962}{\1c&H101010&\3c&H101010&\4c&H101010&\t(0,2000,\1c&HD3F0CB&\3c&H020400&\4c&H000000&)\fad(0,1000)\an2}Shinji Mori\NMakoto Hamaguchi\NMine Shinsuke{NOTE:森信二\\N浜口j誠\\N峯順介}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:31.51,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:750179,751514}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.51,0:12:32.89,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:751514,752890}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:34.35,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:752890,754350}Life is hard, isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:37.14,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:754350,757144}You can't even talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.93,0:12:41.31,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:757937,761315}{\i1}I bet you want to see\Nmy little brother and sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.31,0:12:42.60,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:761315,762608}{\i1}Dad…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:46.65,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:764068,766654}{\i1}Don't worry, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:49.78,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:767363,769782}I will sing for you\Nthe song I composed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:51.65,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:769782,771659}Mine-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.86,0:12:55.95,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:772868,775955}Please make sure to see\Nthe accountant later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.66,0:12:58.45,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:776664,778457}Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.45,0:12:59.62,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:778457,779625}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:01.46,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:780834,781460}See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:04.21,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:782711,784213}I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:11.13,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:788968,791136}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.26,0:13:14.76,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:792263,794765}183,000 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.76,0:13:17.14,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:794765,797142}Are you sure that\Nthere is no mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:20.64,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:797768,800646}As you know, insurance\Ndoesn't cover everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.73,0:13:27.02,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:802731,807027}If you could find the person who hurt your father,\Nthere would be a way to claim damages.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:31.03,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:807736,811031}Is there any chance for you\Nto wait a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:35.24,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:811907,815244}I'm sorry, but we already have\Nextended the deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:40.04,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:816120,820040}Additionally, one of our patients\Nhas filed an official complaint.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:42.83,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:820666,822835}A patient has filed a complaint?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.83,0:13:44.21,Default,Patient,0,0,0,,{TIME:822835,824211}I'm sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:45.29,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:824211,825296}Just a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:48.54,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:825296,828549}We've been criticized several times\Nfor giving you special treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:52.55,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:829341,832553}{\i1}Perhaps that phone call\Nwas made by that patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:57.26,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:833429,837266}I have to ask you to pay the balance\Nwithout any more delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.26,0:13:59.81,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:837266,839810}Otherwise we'll move\Nthe patient to your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:00.97,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:839810,840978}We can't let that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:02.98,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:840978,842980}Please don't call my home just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:04.89,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:842980,844898}I'll work and earn\Nthe money we owe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:05.94,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:844898,845941}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:07.94,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:846775,847943}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:09.57,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:847943,849570}I hope you mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:11.57,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:849570,851572}Yes. You have my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:20.78,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:854325,860789}{\i1}Nozomi slowly began to realize what a heavy blow\Nto the family was her father's hospitalization.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.78,0:14:25.08,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:860789,865085}{\i1}Once again, her hope was\Nshattered by Michiko's scheming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:28.29,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:865628,868297}What's with that serious look\Non your pretty face?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:30.79,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:869340,870799}Stuff happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:33.92,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:870799,873927}If something's worrying you,\Nyour uncle will listen to you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:34.97,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:873927,874970}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.09,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:874970,876096}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:39.80,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:877431,879808}Hey, Nozomi-chan,\Ndon't be so distant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:43.89,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:882603,883896}Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:47.31,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:885564,887316}You're so sweet, Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.31,0:14:49.94,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:887316,889943}You really turned pale at the sight\Nof a little under 20,000 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:52.19,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:889943,892196}Count the zeros again, Kuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:55.44,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:892196,895449}Huh? One, two, three, four…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:58.41,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:895449,898410}Oh, t-that's still just 180,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:01.49,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:898410,901497}I'll be damned.\NCan I keep it for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:04.41,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:901497,904416}Yeah. But keep it from my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.41,0:15:05.91,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:904416,905918}Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.91,0:15:09.46,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:905918,909463}She has enough problems\Nwith her eyes going bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.46,0:15:10.88,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:909463,910881}You're so sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:13.09,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:911548,913092}You're so sweet…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:13.88,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:913092,913884}Kuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:19.34,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:918180,919348}– We're home!\N– We're home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.34,0:15:21.97,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:919348,921975}This place's bustling as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:24.01,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:921975,924019}– Sis!\N– You're home?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:26.77,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:924019,926772}Did you sign any contracts?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.77,0:15:28.10,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:926772,928107}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.10,0:15:29.90,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:928107,929900}When will you release your single?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.94,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:929900,931944}Come on, it's still a long way off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:36.28,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:931944,936281}Before your sister becomes a singer,\Nshe has to learn a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.28,0:15:40.53,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:937282,940536}I understand.\NBut the sooner, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:45.41,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:940536,945416}When Sis becomes a singer,\NMum can finally stop working.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:47.87,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:945416,947876}Kazuo won't have to work, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:50.87,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:948293,950879}Wait, what?\NKazuo, you're working, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:54.46,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:951839,954466}I'm helping with the deliveries\Nin a greengrocer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.46,0:15:56.21,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:954466,956218}What are you going to do\Nwith your savings?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:58.63,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:957010,958637}I'm gonna pay\Nfor the school lunches.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:01.72,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:959596,961724}You can't be the only one of us\Nwho's doing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.77,0:16:10.35,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:968772,970357}{\i1}180,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:13.11,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:970357,973110}{\i1}180,000 yen…\NWhere am I going to find such money?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:14.98,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:973110,974987}{\i1}If only there was\Nsomething I could do…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.98,0:16:16.57,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:974987,976572}Are you still awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:18.49,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:976572,978490}Oh? You can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:20.74,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:978490,980743}I figured by your breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:23.45,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:980743,983454}What are you\Nthinking about so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:25.33,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:983454,985330}A lot of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:28.20,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:985330,988208}I'll go and resume with\NDad's business tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:29.71,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:988208,989710}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:34.17,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:989710,994173}I feel like I'm doing something I like\Nat the expense of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.17,0:16:35.63,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:994173,995632}At our expense?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:38.84,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:996550,998844}That's a huge exaggeration.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:43.59,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:998844,1003599}But I feel so bad that you have to work.\NWhat if you really lose your sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:46.72,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003599,1006727}Stop worrying about\Nwhat you can't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:52.77,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006727,1012775}If you really care for me,\Ndo not give up and keep on studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:57.78,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016320,1017780}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:00.24,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018530,1020240}Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:02.07,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020240,1022075}It's what you wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:05.28,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022075,1025287}I will try harder than ever\Nand become a singer you'll be proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:07.28,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025788,1027289}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:20.34,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1036632,1040344}{\fad(0,1500)}Uchida Productions
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:24.59,Default,Groupies,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043889,1044598}Can I have your sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.59,0:17:26.22,Default,Groupies,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044598,1046225}– Please look over here!\N– We love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.22,0:17:27.39,Default,Groupies,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046225,1047392}They're bringing equipment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.39,0:17:28.85,Default,Groupies,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047392,1048852}I want an autograph so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:34.90,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051980,1054900}Indeed Uchida Productions\Nis a very big company.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:37.90,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054900,1057903}You could say it's a magical castle\Nfor those who want to become famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:41.40,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057903,1061406}But there are only so many people\Nthat are capable of achieving that dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.03,0:17:44.66,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062032,1064660}In order to win\Nin this competitive world,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:48.16,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064660,1068163}you'll need to get rid of your\Nappearance of a daddy's girl first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:50.37,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068163,1070374}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.37,0:17:53.41,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070374,1073418}I feel confident in my ability\Nto stand out from the crowd here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.54,0:17:58.71,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075546,1078715}Neither talent nor financial support\Nwon't be any problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:04.88,Default,Important big guy,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083095,1084888}A student of Master Egawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.88,0:18:06.72,Default,Important big guy,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084888,1086723}Introduced by Nohara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:09.26,Default,Important big guy,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086723,1089268}Born into Kōda family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:11.52,Default,Important big guy,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089268,1091520}What's there not to like?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:17.40,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093772,1097401}Nohara-san, please do not forget\Na small gift from us for the introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.82,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097401,1099820}Mom, this isn't a good place!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:22.03,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099820,1102030}No, it's quite okay, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:24.61,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102030,1104616}It's no secret I never had trouble\Nto accept money from the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:36.12,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114001,1116128}There is something\NI want you to do immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.12,0:18:38.63,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117129,1118630}Again ambushing me\Nout of nowhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:43.46,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120841,1123468}You're afraid that your past\Nwill leak out, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:47.55,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124261,1127556}Well, I don't want to lose\Nmy reputation as a songwriter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:52.64,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128891,1132644}I guess with your reputation it's entirely\Npossible for you to make a nobody into a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:55.64,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133061,1135647}Perhaps. What business\Ndo you have with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:59.86,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136189,1139860}There is someone I'd like you to\Ntake under your wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:00.98,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139860,1140986}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:01.69,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140986,1141695}Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:03.86,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142404,1143864}Mine Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.86,0:19:05.61,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143864,1145616}Huh? That kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.61,0:19:07.20,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145616,1147200}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:10.45,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147200,1150454}You are to listen to me,\Nnot ask questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.45,0:19:13.29,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150454,1153290}Alright. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:15.91,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154249,1155918}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.54,0:19:22.09,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159546,1162090}But we should talk\Nto Mr. Egawa first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:25.38,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163300,1165385}I'll talk to him.\NI'd be surprised if he refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:28.01,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165385,1168013}He let Kōda Miki sign a contract\Nwith Uchida Productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:31.18,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168805,1171183}You have a far greater talent\Nthan she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:34.14,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171183,1174144}If I were to introduce you\Nto a company I have in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:36.73,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174144,1176730}you'd earn about\N300,000 yen to get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:38.48,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176730,1178482}300,000?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:41.44,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178482,1181443}If you like the offer,\Nlet me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.94,0:19:44.19,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182945,1184196}Mr. Nohara!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.19,0:19:45.61,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184196,1185614}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:48.99,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185614,1188992}I thought you hate my guts,\Nand now you're so nice to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:51.53,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189701,1191536}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.53,0:19:54.03,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191536,1194039}As a matter of fact, I'm in desperate\Nneed for that money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:54.99,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194039,1194998}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.99,0:19:57.00,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195999,1197000}Let's work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:13.01,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208470,1213016}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.01,0:20:21.81,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213016,1221817}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:27.19,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224569,1227197}Fantastic! As expected\Nfrom Master Egawa's pupil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:27.90,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227197,1227906}I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.90,0:20:29.44,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227906,1229449}Oh, just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.90,0:20:31.07,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229908,1231076}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:32.45,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231076,1232452}I don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.45,0:20:35.91,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232452,1235914}I did my part by introducing you\Nto this girl and this is where it stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.91,0:20:38.45,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235914,1238458}If there are problems down the road,\NI don't want my name anywhere near it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:43.88,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242254,1243880}Mine-kun. You passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:44.75,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243880,1244756}Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.75,0:20:48.67,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244756,1248677}The contract will be ready in 2-3 days,\Nbut you will have at least 300,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:50.63,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1248677,1250637}For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.63,0:20:52.76,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1250637,1252764}Yes. We'll quickly take care\Nof your stage outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:54.97,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1252764,1254975}You will start\Nyour tour tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:56.97,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255642,1256977}My tour?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.97,0:20:59.10,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256977,1259104}I have to thank Mr. Nohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.10,0:21:00.06,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1259104,1260063}Oh, let's slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.06,0:21:01.98,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260063,1261982}I'll relay it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:04.69,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1261982,1264693}He's very busy\Nand has already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:06.48,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264693,1266486}I wanted to say it personally…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:09.03,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266486,1269031}No worries.\NYou can do it anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:11.19,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269031,1271199}But now, better think of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.19,0:21:14.24,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271199,1274244}You're about to make\Nyour debut on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.24,0:21:16.70,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1274244,1276705}It will be the beginning\Nof a your beautiful career.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:17.99,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276705,1277998}Career?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.99,0:21:20.79,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277998,1280792}{\i1}I'll be able to pay\Nfor Dad's treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.79,0:21:22.37,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1280792,1282377}{\i1}And I'll become a singer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:42.77,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1299728,1302773}{\i1}There are so many people\Ncontracted by DM Productions…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.98,0:21:49.52,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1307986,1309529}{\i1}They look like businessmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.78,0:21:56.53,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1315786,1316536}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.53,0:21:58.58,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1316536,1318580}Nozomi-chan… Nozomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.99,0:22:03.16,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1320999,1323168}Ah, Kuma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.16,0:22:04.50,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1323168,1324503}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.29,0:22:08.17,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1326296,1328173}I feel so ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.17,0:22:10.63,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1328173,1330634}What's happened, Kuma-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.63,0:22:14.55,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330634,1334554}I haven't been able\Nto raise any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.55,0:22:17.14,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1334554,1337140}Now you're forced to leave\Nand won't be able to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.72,0:22:20.14,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1337724,1340143}Kuma-san, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.68,0:22:23.06,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1340685,1343063}This is something\NI've decided for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.93,0:22:25.56,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1343939,1345565}You're just trying to comfort me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.44,0:22:27.85,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1346441,1347859}No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.85,0:22:32.57,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1347859,1352572}I assure you, singing in front of a new audience\Nwill surely be a good experience for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.32,0:22:34.57,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1353323,1354574}Nozomi-chan…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.20,0:22:37.07,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1355200,1357077}Come on, stand up, Kuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.49,0:22:38.82,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1357494,1358829}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.82,0:22:41.58,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1358829,1361581}You're always so kind to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:44.08,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1362040,1364084}Thank you, Kuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:49.92,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1366962,1369923}Take care of my folks for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.92,0:22:51.55,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1369923,1371550}Sure thing. Don't worry.
